{"tid":2422410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★聶德權鼓勵公務員盡早接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:50:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"12a5ddbdeaef748712397868a269ef0a84be1f65","tid":2422410,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局長聶德權向全體公務員發信，表示行政長官及司局長在剛過去的星期一已接種科興疫苗，過程簡單順利，沒有任何不適，鼓勵公務員盡早接種疫苗，又說政府已邀請專家研究過往多種防疫措施，例如院舍的探訪、檢測次數、檢疫安排、社交距離及出行通關等，之後會否有條件鬆綁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577472-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577472-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=9fc69483\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577472-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=44cd887e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577472-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c77c443a3e74a1cb82eea745373f730ccf467f53","tid":2422410,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358ec02b520b3ae48d9da27dca1370edd3377662","tid":2422410,"uid":284855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"燒唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 